            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Small business: $79–$199/mo (NiceJob, Grade.us). Mid-size: $229–$449/mo (Birdeye, Podium). Enterprise: $499+/mo per location (Reputation.com, Yext). For done-for-you local SEO with review monitoring included, theStacc Local SEO is $49/mo.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Is SMS or email better for review requests?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>SMS wins on conversion — 5–10x higher response rate than email — but is more expensive per send and has stricter compliance rules (TCPA in the US). Email is cheaper and easier but converts lower. Most platforms support both; ideal is SMS first, email follow-up.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Can I use Google Business Profile for review management?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes for free monitoring and responses on Google reviews specifically. GBP has no review request, no multi-platform aggregation, and no automation. For under 30 reviews a month on Google only, GBP is enough. Above that or for cross-platform, you need a dedicated tool.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What's the difference between review generation and review monitoring?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Generation = actively requesting new reviews via SMS or email (Podium, NiceJob). Monitoring = tracking and responding to reviews that already exist across platforms (ReviewTrackers, Reputation.com). Most modern platforms do both, but with different strengths.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
